  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "* We acknowledge that we are gathered on the traditional and unceded territory of the Algonquin Anishinaabe Nation.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "For generations, they have been the stewards of this land, and their deep connection to it continues to this day.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "We recognize the enduring presence and contributions of the Algonquin people to this region.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "We also acknowledge the painful history of colonization and the displacement of Indigenous communities from their ancestral lands.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "We commit ourselves to learning, understanding, and honoring the Algonquin Nation's history and culture.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "We recognize the importance of working collaboratively to create a more just and equitable future for all who call this land home.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "* Nous reconnaissons que nous sommes réunis sur le territoire traditionnel et non cédé de la nation algonquine anishinaabe.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "Depuis des générations, ils sont les gardiens de cette terre et le lien profond qui les unit à elle perdure encore aujourd'hui.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "Nous reconnaissons la présence et les contributions durables du peuple algonquin dans cette région.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "Nous reconnaissons également l'histoire douloureuse de la colonisation et du déplacement des communautés autochtones de leurs terres ancestrales.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "Nous nous engageons à apprendre, à comprendre et à honorer l'histoire et la culture de la nation algonquine.",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
  {
    "section_type": "land_ack",
    "type": "minutes_chunk",
    "document_type": "minutes",
    "document_subtype": "officer",
    "source_file": "August 14 _ Officer Meeting.txt",
    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "Nous reconnaissons l'importance de travailler en collaboration pour créer un avenir plus juste et plus équitable pour tous ceux qui vivent sur cette terre.\n________________",
    "meeting_date": "2025-08-14",
    "meeting_date_display": "Aug 14, 2025"
  },
